hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 写出密度函数：

$$
\rho_{NKG}(r) = N_{tot}\,\frac{5}{4\pi R_M^2}\,\bigl(\frac{r}{R_M}\bigr)^{-1}\bigl(1+\frac{r}{R_M}\bigr)^{-3.5}
$$
$$
\rho_{scatt}(r) = N_{tot}\,\frac{R_M^2}{4\pi\,r^4}
$$

2. 构建比值：

$$
R = \frac{\rho_{scatt}(r)}{\rho_{NKG}(r)}
= \frac{N_{tot}\,\frac{R_M^2}{4\pi\,r^4}}
       {N_{tot}\,\frac{5}{4\pi R_M^2}\,\bigl(\frac{r}{R_M}\bigr)^{-1}\bigl(1+\frac{r}{R_M}\bigr)^{-3.5}}
$$

3. 化简：

$$
R = \frac{R_M^2}{r^4} \cdot \frac{4\pi R_M^2}{5} \cdot \frac{r}{R_M} \cdot \left(1+\frac{r}{R_M}\right)^{3.5}
= \frac{1}{5}\,\Bigl(\frac{R_M}{r}\Bigr)^3\,\left(1+\frac{r}{R_M}\right)^{3.5}
$$

4. 当 $r=5R_M$ 时，$\frac{r}{R_M}=5$，所以

$$
R = \frac{1}{5}\,\Bigl(\frac{1}{5}\Bigr)^3\,(1+5)^{3.5}
= \frac{1}{625}\,6^{3.5}
= \frac{216\sqrt{6}}{625}
$$
